SAK-11824

Portal My Active Sites: Fixes a bug in IE 6 where some form controls show through the My Active Sites drop down menu when it is active. This fix uses an MIT-licensed fucntion written by Brandon Aaron, which hacks around the underlying bug in jQuery using an invisible iFrame.

Patch from Eli Cochran.

SAK-11824

Portal My Active Sites: Fixes a bug in IE 6 where some form controls show through the My Active Sites drop down menu when it is active. This fix uses an MIT-licensed fucntion written by Brandon Aaron, which hacks around the underlying bug in jQuery using an invisible iFrame.

Patch from Eli Cochran.
